Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:34.09,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}扭曲的覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去結花有可能去的地方看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:01:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能已經晚了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.31,0:02:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢久前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  衣服都打爛了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點出乎意料  那傢伙還挺強的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說讓她給逃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說晚了  是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…  結花的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪兒撿的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西在哪兒撿到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直慘不忍睹啊  保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君變了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君…我的驅君…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保健室全毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花…結花！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點  驅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花不在這  沒有血的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:04:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能斷定她沒事  不過看來是逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就時間而言還不會跑得太遠  分頭找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很危險  不過也沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子  菊理  我們各自搜查學校周邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅和賢久消耗過大 一邊恢復體力一邊搜索校內吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擅自做主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是發現結花  就立刻回到學校裡  和驅他們集合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到賢久發出的火柱就全員回到學校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點小事你不會推辭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  隊長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅也同意吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  出發
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  為了朋友和明日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了朋友和明日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花  結花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花  結花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著到體育館找
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯  要是那時候我沒把結花一人丟下的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要平安啊  結花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉  別生氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅  你對女孩子的心意全盤托出還真不害臊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  我只是在想  要是那傢伙也消失了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能不能像你這麼拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子跟我有著同樣的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她的笑容反而讓我看著心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺她背負著罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:07:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要問了  要是知道我至今為止做過的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢久前輩也一定會改觀的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密  要是讓你擔心的話我會很難相處的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒出息  反而讓她擔心我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幫臭蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別偷聽人家的秘密談話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  去找小公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在靠近地面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花  迷路了的結花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是聽到的話就精神地回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了驅君  你喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我也給你做便當來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君  你喜歡我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡驅君了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是狡猾的魔女  趁我不在就垂死掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯佩爾比亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劫之眼的主人和「碎片」們的處理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給你和因威迪亞和斯高拉諦加了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  阿瓦利提亞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎  因威迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼狽的敗北和那被燒毀的醜陋的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能做的事也只有一件了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花  你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點回去的話  大家都會擔心的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:10:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  有個好消息帶給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊理學姐把黑騎士打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊理學姐的能力很強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有著強力的能力  拼命戰鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用為這種事發愁啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花不適合戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我沒能力  驅君才遠離我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼傻話呢  驅前輩不是一直都火熱超級愛著你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩之所以戰鬥也是為了保護結花哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你到底有多迷人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:10:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就告訴結花吧  我的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到日本的爺爺來接我之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生活在一個叫德拉斯貝尼亞的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從我懂事以來  世界就是地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血債血償永無止境的民族戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在破壞和虐殺的暴風雨中  無論是誰都拿起武器奮戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女老少都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我有死不了的身子  就算自爆啊踩地雷了都會再生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以被當成人體兵器肆意使用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人和夥伴們都陸續被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也不停不停不停地殺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了朋友和明日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這句話支撐著我的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人格和戰鬥能力都是在那地獄養成的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法保護夥伴  和明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不用眼鏡封印起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可就會變成一個超危險的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓結花你也變成我這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥能力什麼的  還是不要覺醒的好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  驅前輩也一定會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子  沒事了  已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無法逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什麼啊？  這光柱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為不死人偶與我並肩戰鬥的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯高拉諦加
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那收納你的  名喚作艾克迪亞的容器  已然不復存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯高拉諦加…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑騎士被…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你這混帳  煩死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:15:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區碎片  竟傷我尊嚴  殘我軀體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此罪  須以命償之
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠什麼吠  我叫你報仇不成反送小命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說  可我這邊也快吃不消了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  驅？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來只有一戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就先上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美鈴前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因威迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別顧慮什麼  全力一戰便是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我快點趕回來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子  橘前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪兒了  到底去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是草壁五寶之一  火車切廣光對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀勢是草壁流  你果然是草壁一族的陰陽師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:16:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這你怎麼會知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竟然要和草壁家的劍士對決
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是造化弄人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草壁二刀斬的架勢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撐…  撐不住了  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些碎片的罪孽…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要魂飛魄散才能贖清
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強的殺氣…  寸步難移…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是何方神聖？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:18:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間快到了  你們本就不該存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.66,0:18:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不對…  沒有這種可能的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝之狀態無法戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾名  斯佩爾比亞  此戰  日後再分勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就交給你了  因威迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美鈴前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要封印我們的結界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡…儘管殺我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想要自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.81,0:19:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.99,0:19:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劫之眼的主人  還有碎片們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起化為塵埃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰…  驅君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是結花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消  消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的毀滅之力…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.69,0:20:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花到底都做了些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕  是她所放射出來的光芒  使力量無效化了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花她…  覺醒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強啊  結花這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但同時也是危險的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅是敵人的  就連我們的力量  也被無效化了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  驅君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.87,0:21:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會保護好你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以求你了  只對我一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只對我一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人  你們騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維拉德他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.91,0:22:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪不可赦…  絕不原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.54,0:22:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要毀滅你  這個污穢的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這便是  維拉德與我  莉澤特的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.02,0:23:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.52,0:23:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我並不希望你覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.13,0:24:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不希望你被捲入戰鬥之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.19,0:24:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.91,0:24:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花她的情況還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.73,0:24:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}讓惡魔覺醒的就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.95,0:24:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.28,0:24:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.05,0:24:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢魔之時
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.40,0:24:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢久  去吃烤肉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.47,0:24:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛背肉  里脊肉  特別降價
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.86,0:24:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便山吃海喝  爽得很
